                 +5V
                  |
      --------------------------------
      |        |           |        |
    DHT11    Soil        Flame    Arduino
     VCC       VCC         VCC
      |         |           |
     GND-------GND---------GND

DHT DATA  → D2
Soil AO   → A0
Flame DO  → D3

ESP8266:

3.3V  → VCC
GND   → GND
3.3V  → EN
TX    → Arduino Pin 10
RX    → Arduino Pin 11 (via voltage divider)
